text:
Influenza vs #COVID19:

Influenza: Children are important drivers of influenza virus transmission in the community

COVID-19: Initial data indicates that children are less affected than adults & that clinical attack rates in the 0-19 age group are low

#coronavirus https://t.co/DnZmTJHoOv
